'''CRI Vientiane at 93.0 FM''' is a radio station in [[Vientiane]], [[Laos]]. It is part of [[China Radio International]]. It broadcasts primarily in [[English language|English]]. According to [[China Radio International]], this is the third overseas radio station launch after [[CRI 91.9 FM|CRI Nairobi Kenya 91.9 FM]].<ref>[http://www.franzbleeker.de/radio.html China´s and Laotian heads of state push the starting button]</ref><ref>[http://enmms.chinabroadcast.cn/messenger/2007/200701.pdf CRI Launches Vientiane 93.0 FM in The Capital of Laos] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707013642/http://enmms.chinabroadcast.cn/messenger/2007/200701.pdf |date=2011-07-07 }}</ref>
