{{About|the South African channel|the Australian channel that used to be known as GO!|9Go!}}
{{Unreferenced|date=July 2013}}

'''Go''' was a TV channel on the [[DStv]] satellite network. The channel was broadcast on DStv channel 84. After a channel shuffle by DStv in October 2007, Go was moved to channel 123. Go was a channel for preteens, teens and twenty-somethings.

On 23 June 2009, Go was closed down and was replaced on Wednesday 1 July 2009 at 5:00pm with [[Vuzu]]. Much of Go's programming was transferred to Vuzu.

