==Overview== The hospital is open 24/7.<ref name=centreoverview>{{cite web|title=Overview: The Centre Hospitalier Princesse Grace (CHPG)|url=http://www.chpg.mc/en/hospital-center/hospital-center/overview|website=Centre hospitalier Princesse Grace|accessdate=December 26, 2015}}</ref> It is the only public hospital in Monaco.<ref name=centreoverview/> It has 210 beds for patients.<ref name=centreoverview/> It is non-smoking.<ref name=centreoverview/>
